Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.38,0:21:10.13,*Default,,0,0,0,,你有筆嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.68,0:21:11.27,*Default,,0,0,0,,給你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.55,0:21:12.27,*Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.02,0:21:16.87,*Default,,0,0,0,,好  就這樣吧
