Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.19,0:21:21.80,*Default,,0,0,0,,我不是回來  是重新加入
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.31,0:21:23.13,*Default,,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.50,0:21:25.19,*Default,,0,0,0,,也就是說  你是新部員囉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.72,0:21:26.31,*Default,,0,0,0,,是哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.38,0:21:28.58,*Default,,0,0,0,,從今天開始請叫我真白前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.85,0:21:29.61,*Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.93,0:21:34.91,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs22}無敵的翅膀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.95,0:21:38.04,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs22}追逐星辰
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.34,0:21:44.08,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs22}答案一定在天空中
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.37,0:21:50.37,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs22}無限的世界衝破黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.59,0:21:58.85,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs22}響徹天際的意志  就是天空霸者Zephilion
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.23,0:21:38.56,*Default,,0,0,0,,這個就是Zehilion？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.60,0:21:40.06,*Default,,0,0,0,,學姐  說錯啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.07,0:21:41.42,*Default,,0,0,0,,這樣可算不上ZePhilion
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.49,0:21:46.49,*Default,,0,0,0,,明日香頭上的翅膀原來是JePhilion的翅膀啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.56,0:21:48.23,*Default,,0,0,0,,還是錯了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.48,0:21:51.13,*Default,,0,0,0,,這是小的時候  島上的一個孩子給我的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.69,0:21:52.74,*Default,,0,0,0,,島上的孩子？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.99,0:21:54.03,*Default,,0,0,0,,會是誰呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.20,0:21:57.40,*Default,,0,0,0,,像是女版的教練…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.93,0:21:58.59,*Default,,0,0,0,,好噁心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.89,0:22:00.85,*Default,,0,0,0,,小時候的事情嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.29,0:22:05.88,*Default,,0,0,0,,說起來也有點像我以前挑戰過的孩子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.45,0:22:08.43,*Default,,0,0,0,,不會是同一個人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.43,0:22:11.70,*Default,,0,0,0,,不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.56,0:22:13.77,*Default,,0,0,0,,管他呢
