Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.27,0:23:50.34,*Default,,0,0,0,,6點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.53,0:23:51.23,*Default,,0,0,0,,教練
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.11,0:23:54.06,*Default,,0,0,0,,這也是為了FC嗎？
